  <thing id="cMPSGGChar" name="Charming" description="When dealing with subjects that are of at least indifferent attitude toward them (not unfriendly or hostile) while in a calm environment, the luminary adds half their class level to Charisma checks and Charisma-based skill checks.\n\nThis environment must be one where distractions or stress would not prevent them from taking 10 on a skill check if they wished to.\n\nThe luminary has a bright smile, quick wit, dulcet laugh, or is otherwise just a delight to be in the presence of during social events." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Add half levels to Charisma checks and Charisma-based skill checks" uniqueness="unique">
