  <thing id="cMPSGGComp" name="Compelling" description="The luminary&apos;s personality is even more magnetic than it appears at first glance. The luminary may use an ability that has uses per day based on their Charisma bonus or modifier without it counting against their daily limit.\n\nSuch abilities include the influence class feature, or the catharsis talent.\n\nThis feature may be used once per day, and they gain an additional free use of one of their Charisma powers for every 3 luminary levels." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Gain additional uses of Charisma based talents a number of times a day" uniqueness="unique">
