  <thing id="cMPSGGSiOf" name="Shrug It Off" description="As a standard action, the luminary can convince an injured ally that the harm the ally sustained is not as serious as it first appeared, allowing the ally to access greater reserves of endurance and drive. This restores hp to the Ally.\n\nMinimum of 1d6 hp of damage healed, with an additional 1d6 at 3rd level and every two levels thereafter. A creature cannot be healed above 50% of its hit point total by a use of shrug it off, and a creature can only benefit from a specific luminary&apos;s shrug it off once per day.\n\nA luminary may use shrug it off a number of times per day equal to their Charisma bonus (minimum 1/day)." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
