  <thing id="cMPSGGInLt" name="Inner Light" description="A celebrity has a special force of personality that is noticed by those around her, though they can never quite define or explain it. \n\nThe celebrity treats her Charisma modifier as being 1 higher than its actual value for purposes of ability checks, skill checks, feats, and extraordinary and supernatural abilities (but not spells, spellcasting, or spell-like abilities). \n\nThis increases by +1 every 8 levels." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Treats her Charisma modifier as being 1 higher every 8 levels" uniqueness="unique">
