  <thing id="cMPSGGBnPf" name="Born Performer" description="The headliner is a natural performer, and excels at making money and using theater and misdirection to fool observers. \n\nThe headliner is treated as having Profession (stage performer) with a number of ranks equal to his level. \n\nHe also adds one third his level (minimum +1) to Acrobatics, Appraise, Bluff, Climb, Disable Device, Disguise, Escape Artist, Handle Animal, Perform, Profession, Sleight of Hand, Stealth, and Use Magic Device" compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
